§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ An ❬orthonormal family of vectors❭ in an inner product space
    is a family of vectors with unit norm. ⦉
⦉

¶ ⦊
  ‖ \begin{proposition} ⦉

  ‖ An orthogonal family of vectors can be made orthonormal. ⦉

  ‖ \end{proposition} ⦉
